Package com.payd.shooti.gamemap.background

Enum Class EParallax

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<EParallax>
com.payd.shooti.gamemap.background.EParallax
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<EParallax>, Constable
public enum EParallax extends Enum<EParallax>
Parallax asset names start as "0.png" and go up to "N.png" where N is the number of layers. If LabDay has 5 layers, that means there are 6 images in the "labday" directory, starting at 0.
